Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.42,0:40:05.48,1080,,0,0,0,,Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.30,0:40:07.10,1080,,0,0,0,,Minato...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.08,0:40:08.46,1080,,0,0,0,,Byl tam...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.96,0:40:09.96,1080,,0,0,0,,K čertu, o kom mluvíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.38,0:40:11.98,1080,,0,0,0,,Hej! Jsi v pořádku?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.08,0:40:12.40,1080,,0,0,0,,Počkej!
